dc_title_s: Hudson River New York Harbor, 2 sheets, sheet no. 2, from Edgewater to Bloomers, Harbor Lines from surveys of 1911-13
dc_description_s: Map of proposed pierhead and bulkhead lines in the Hudson River, Bergen County, New Jersey from Edgewater to Bloomers; also adjacent shoreline of New York City, New York|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Map is drawn from a composite of measurements from other charts from 1902 - 1912
